//9.完整示例
<a href="mailto:863139978@qq.com;384900096@qq.com?cc=zhangqian0406@yeah.net&bcc=993233461@qq.com&subject=[邮件主题]&body=腾讯诚邀您参与%0A%0Ahttp://www.baidu.com%0A%0A<img src='images/1.jpg' />">点击我发邮件</a>
